to do until help arrives.

300
00:17:55,970 --> 00:17:59,500
Then we'll have to decide who's going where.

301
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:01,220
Why don't we use these?

302
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:02,970
They're playing cards.

303
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:08,230
