spades, hearts, diamonds, and clubs.

306
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,460
Sounds good to me.

307
00:18:14,460 --> 00:18:15,530
Hold on.

308
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:20,400
There's an odd stain on the top card.

309
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:24,080
What if you already know what
it is without turning it over?

310
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:26,370
I-I haven't done anything like that.

311
00:18:26,370 --> 00:18:28,800
Who cares? It's just a game, right?

312
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:32,060
It may be a game, but I want to do it right.

313
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:35,880
