using the number of lines.

315
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:42,000
Then how about rock-paper-scissors?

316
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:46,810
This is just like that time you guys
had to decide who'd be the captain.

317
00:18:49,460 --> 00:18:51,270
You're right.

318
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:54,380
Then let's do what we did back then.

319
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:56,900
